Voyager New Moves

Withdraw

Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
20 0 Withdraws the body into its hard shell to raise Defense and Sp. Def.

Details

In Pokemon Voyager, this move raises Sp. Def as well as Defense, and PP is reduced to 20.
